creator: Abuzz
descriptionHtml:
Soap bubbles are delightful to watch and entertaining to create for children of all age - from a baby to older school kids. This is an innovative baby game that is a brilliant combination of entertainment and learning. In this free game, find bubbles in all shapes and sizes, which you can play with. You don’t need a “bubble solution”; but only this bubble game packed with multiple activities to make as many bubble balloons as you want. Playing with bubbles is a wonderful way to encourage many areas of development and early learning in a baby. It encourages finger isolation, visual scanning, attention memory, and hand-eye coordination - all of which are very important for children at an early age.

Features:
Bath time with rubber duck or a toy boat or a fish. It is the most common place where kids play with soap bubbles. Just make a splash and see how new bubbles emerge from the foam.

Bubble toy gun with cute animal shapes. Inflate hundreds of bubbles per minute. Play with the dolphin or the cute elephant and see how they make never-ending bubbles with a single tap.

Colorful bubble wands with different shapes. Select your favorite shape and blow continuous bubbles in the shapes of circle, heart, and star. Then use your little fingers and start popping them one by one.

Bubble machine that makes a giant bubble. A bubble maker that creates the biggest balloons that pop into smaller ones - watch them as they fly away and try to catch as many as you can.

30 languages and pronunciations will help your children develop their speech and learn first words. Learn the names of farm animals, jungle animals, fruits, vegetables, alphabets, numbers, cars, shapes, and kindergarten stationary. Languages include English, Arabic, Spanish, French, German, Portuguese, Turkish, Russian, Indonesian and many more.


If you have any feedback and suggestions on how we could further improve the design and interaction of our games, please visit our website www.iabuzz.com or leave us a message at kids@iabuzz.com
